lenders.name: Nineteen Eleven
lenders.loan_because: Nineteen Eleven is pleased to present our funding in the loving memory of those in our community that are no longer with us: Nick "Oxossi" Coppola , Jeff Kimbro, Jason "spG" Bednarz, Jeremy 'Parasite' Stella, and Andrew "Beach" Brennan.
lenders.occupational_info:
Nineteen Eleven is the original home of the competitive Day of Defeat 1.3 community.

Launched in early 2002, Nineteen Eleven quickly became the go to source for clan news, match predictions, movies, and community discussion.

Much of the success of both DoD 1.3 and DoD Source is owed to the 1911 community and their push for competitive game-play in the early years of DoD.

In 2004, the site was absorbed into GotFrag.

Recently relaunched (February 2011), Nineteen Eleven has once again been adopted by the remaining Day of Defeat 1.3 community, and serves as a the virtual hub for news, league predictions, movies, and community discussion.
